nt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKash%20is%20a%20brilliant%20lawyer%2C%20investigator%2C%20and%20'America%20First'%20fighter%20who%20has%20spent%20his%20career%20exposing%20corruption%2C%20defending%20Justice%2C%20and%20protecting%20the%20American%20People%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trump%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20his%20social%20media%20platform.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident-elect%20Trump%20praised%20Mr%20Patel's%20contributions%20during%20his%20first%20term%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20exposing%20the%20%26quot%3BRussia%20Hoax.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patel's%20nomination%20also%20signals%20Mr%20Trump's%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20current%20FBI%20leadership%20under%20Christopher%20Wray%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20appointed%20in%202017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20has%20openly%20criticised%20Mr%20Wray's%20handling%20of%20the%20FBI%2C%20particularly%20its%20investigations%20involving%20Mr%20Trump%20himself.%20Under%20Mr%20Wray's%20tenure%2C%20the%20FBI%20conducted%20a%20court-approved%20search%20at%20Mr%20Trump's%20Mar-a-Lago%20estate%20in%20Florida%20in%20connection%20with%20classified%20documents%2C%20a%20move%20that%20enraged%20the%20former%20president%20and%20his%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patel%2C%2044%2C%20has%20made%20no%20secret%20of%20his%20desire%20to%20overhaul%20the%20FBI.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20conservative%20Shawn%20Ryan%20Show%2C%20Mr%20Patel%20proposed%20radical%20changes%2C%20including%20dismantling%20the%20FBI's%20intelligence-gathering%20operations%20and%20repurposing%20its%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20problem%20the%20FBI%20has%20had%20has%20come%20out%20of%20its%20intel%20shops.%20I'd%20break%20that%20component%20out%20of%20it.%20I'd%20shut%20down%20the%20FBI%20Hoover%20building%20on%20day%20one%20and%20reopen%20it%20the%20next%20day%20as%20a%20museum%20of%20the%20deep%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patel%20declared.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I'd%20take%20the%207%2C000%20employees%20that%20work%20in%20that%20building%20and%20send%20them%20across%20America%20to%20chase%20down%20criminals.%20Go%20be%20cops.%20You're%20cops.%20Go%20be%20cops.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patel%20would%20work%20under%20Mr%20Trump's%20proposed%20Attorney%20General%2C%20Pam%20Bondi%2C%20to%20restore%20what%20Mr%20Trump%20described%20as%20the%20FBI's%20original%20ethos%3A%20Fidelity%2C%20Bravery%2C%20and%20Integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKash%20Patel's%20Journey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patel%20was%20born%20in%20Queens%2C%20New%20York%2C%20to%20parents%20of%20Gujarati%20descent%20who%20emigrated%20from%20East%20Africa.%20After%20earning%20his%20law%20degree%2C%20Mr%20Patel%20worked%20as%20a%20public%20defender%20in%20Florida%2C%20representing%20clients%20in%20state%20and%20federal%20courts.%20He%20later%20joined%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20as%20a%20prosecutor%2C%20handling%20high-profile%20international%20terrorism%20cases%20across%20East%20Africa%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patel's%20career%20took%20a%20turn%20when%20he%20joined%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20as%20a%20civilian%20lawyer.%20There%2C%20he%20collaborated%20with%20Special%20Operations%20Command%2C%20focusing%20on%20global%20counterterrorism%20operations.%20His%20work%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20Congressman%20Devin%20Nunes%2C%20then-chair%20of%20the%20House%20Intelligence%20Committee%2C%20who%20recruited%20him%20as%20senior%20counsel%20on%20counterterrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20In%20The%20Trump%20Administration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patel%20rose%20to%20prominence%20during%20Mr%20Trump's%20first%20term%20and%20was%20part%20of%20the%20House%20Republicans'%20investigation%20into%20the%20FBI's%20handling%20of%20the%20Russia%20probe.%20He%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20drafting%20the%20controversial%20GOP%20memo%20which%20alleged%20bias%20in%20