e%20AI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFunding%20in%20the%20space%20grew%20fivefold%20from%202022%20to%202023%20alone%2C%20according%20to%20CB%20Insights.%20The%20biggest%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20generative%20AI%20boom%20have%20been%20the%20biggest%20companies.%20Tech%20companies%20on%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20have%20seen%20a%2030%25%20gain%20since%20January%202022%2C%20compared%20to%20only%2015%25%20for%20small-cap%20companies%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-questions-consulting-firms-are-answering-for-clients-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsulting%20firms%20are%20expecting%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20up%20an%20increasing%20portion%20of%20their%20revenue.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-explained-mckinsey-bain-bcg-compare-big-three-strategy-consultants-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoston%20Consulting%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%20generates%20a%20fifth%20of%20its%20revenue%20from%20AI%2C%20and%20much%20of%20that%20work%20involves%20advising%20clients%20on%20generative%20AI%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Almost%2040%25%20of%20McKinsey's%20work%20now%20comes%20from%20AI%2C%20and%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20that%20is%20moving%20to%20generative%20AI%2C%20Ben%20Ellencweig%2C%20a%20senior%20partner%20who%20leads%20alliances%2C%20acquisitions%2C%20and%20partnerships%20globally%20for%20McKinsey's%20AI%20arm%2C%20QuantumBlack%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmaller%20companies%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20rely%20on%20larger%20ones%2C%20either%20by%20building%20applications%20on%20existing%20large%20language%20models%20or%20waiting%20for%20their%20next%20major%20developer%20tool%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20young%20developers%20are%20optimistic%20that%20ChatGPT%20will%20level%20the%20playing%20field%20and%20believe%20it's%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20they%20catch%20up%20to%20bigger%20