erations-after-israeli-strike%2Famp_articleshow%2F115849694.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTipu%20Sultan%20Is%20Actually%20A%20Very%20Complex%20Figure%20In%20History%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20(EAM)%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Saturday%20attended%20the%20launch%20of%20Indian%20historian%20Vikram%20Sampath's%20book%20'Tipu%20Sultan%3A%20The%20Saga%20of%20the%20Mysore%20Interregnum'%20at%20the%20Indian%20Habitat%20Centre%20here%20in%20Delhi.%20S%20Jaishankar%20described%20Tipu%20Sultan%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20complex%20figure%20in%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20highlighting%20both%20his%20resistance%20to%20British%20colonial%20control%20and%20the%20controversial%20aspects%20of%20his%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20event%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTipu%20Sultan%20is%20actually%20a%20very%2C%20very%20complex%20figure%20in%20history.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20he%20has%20the%20reputation%20as%20a%20key%20figure%20who%20resisted%20the%20British%20colonial%20control%20over%20India%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20fact%20that%20his%20defeat%20and%20death%20can%20be%20considered%20a%20turning%20point%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20fate%20of%20peninsular%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20also%20noted%20the%20%26quot%3Badverse%26quot%3B%20effects%20of%20Tipu%20Sultan's%20rule%20in%20the%20Mysore%20region.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20evokes%20strong%20adverse%20sentiments%20even%20today%20in%20many%20regions%2C%20some%20in%20Mysore%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%20further%20emphasized%20that%20Indian%20history%20has%20focused%20more%20on%20Tipu%20Sultan's%20battles%20with%20the%20British%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bunderplaying%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bneglecting%26quot%3B%20other%20aspects%20of%20his%20rule.%20%26quot%3BContemporary%20history%20writing%2C%20certainly%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20has%20focused%20largely%20on%20the%20former%2C%20and%20underplaying%2C%20if%20not%20neglecting%20the%20later.%20Let's%20be%20honest%2C%20this%20was%20not%20an%20accident%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20History%20is%20complicated%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bcherry-picking%20of%20facts%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Tipu%20Sultan%20has%20led%20to%20the%20advancement%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20narrative%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistory%2C%20in%20all%20societies%2C%20is%20complicated%2C%20and%20politics%20indulges%20in%20cherry-picking%20the%20facts.%20This%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Tipu%20Sultan.%20By%20highlighting%20the%20Tipu-English%20binary%2C%20to%20the%20exclusion%20of%20a%20more%20complicated%20reality%2C%20a%20particular%20narrative%20has%20been%20advanced%20over%20the%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%20reaffirmed%20that%20under%20PM%20Modi's%20government%2C%20India%20has%20seen%20the%20emergence%20of%20alternative%20perspectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20changes%20in%20our%20political%20dispensation%20have%20led%20to%20the%20emergence%20of%20alternative%20perspectives.%20We%20are%20no%20longer%20prisoners%20of%20a%20vote%20bank%2C%20nor%20it%20is%20politically%20incorrect%20to%20bring%20out%20inconvenient%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20further%20about%20the%20book%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20someone%20from%20the%20diplomatic%20world%2C%20I%20was%20really%20struck%20by%20info%20and%20insights%20which%20are%20provided%20in%20this%20volume%20on%20Tipu%20Sultan.%20We%20in%20India%20have%20tendered%20to%20mainly%20study%20post-independence%20foreign%20policy%20--%20perhaps%20this%20too%20was%20a%20conscious%20choice.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20many%20of%20our%20kingdoms%20and%20states%20forayed%20into%20international%20affairs%20in%20previous%20centuries%20in%20pursuance%20of%20thier%20particular%20interests%2C%20and%20some%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20continued%20to%20do%20so%20even%20till%20independence.%20The%20interaction%20of%20Tipu's%20missionary%20with%20their%20French%20and%20English%20counterparts%20is%20really%20fascinating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%20concluded%20by%20saying%20that%20open-minded%20scholarship%20and%20genuine%20debate%20are%20central%20to%20India's%20evolution%20as%20a%20pluralistic%20society%20and%20vibrant%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732988220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F8kbgqofo_s-jaishankar_625x300_30_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftipu-sultan-is-actually-a-very-complex-figure-in-history-s-jaishankar-7143362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22External%20Affairs%20Minister%20(EAM)%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Saturday%20attended%20the%20launch%20of%20Indian%20historian%20Vikram%20Sampath's%20book%20'Tipu%20Sultan%3A%20The%20Saga%20of%20the%20Mysore%20Interregnum'%20at%20the%20Indian%20Habitat%20Centre%20here%20in%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Production%20Biz%20Powwow%20Focus%20Returns%20to%20London%20With%20Key%20Format%20Changes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732987912000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLOTR_S2_UT_221025_00250_R2_3000.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236231474%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Focus%2C%20the%20end-of-year%20meeting%20place%20for%20the%20international%20production%20community%2C%20ret