20the%20status%20quo.%20The%20story%2C%20he%20said%2C%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20%26quot%3Bwho%20I%20was%20to%20become%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adani%2C%20who%20delivered%20the%20keynote%20address%20at%20the%2051st%20India%20Gem%20and%20Jewellery%20Awards%20in%20Jaipur%20this%20evening%2C%20said%20that%20diamond%20trading%20was%20his%20entry%20point%20into%20his%20journey%20to%20becoming%20an%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20year%201978%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2016%2C%20I%20left%20my%20school%2C%20left%20my%20home%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20and%20took%20a%20one-way%20ticket%20to%20Mumbai.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20I%20would%20do%20but%20I%20was%20clear%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20entrepreneur.%20And%20I%20believed%20Mumbai%20was%20the%20city%20of%20opportunities%20that%20would%20give%20me%20this%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20recalled%20the%20%26quot%3Bjoy%26quot%3B%20of%20closing%20his%20first%20deal%20and%20commission%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20my%20first%20opportunity%20at%20Mahendra%20Brothers%2C%20where%20I%20learned%20the%20art%20of%20diamond%20assorting.%20Even%20today%2C%20I%20recall%20the%20joy%20of%20closing%20my%20first%20deal.%20It%20was%20a%20transaction%20with%20a%20Japanese%20buyer%20and%20I%20got%20a%20commission%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20That%20day%20marked%20the%20start%20of%20a%20journey%20that%20would%20shape%20the%20way%20I%20would%20live%20my%20life%20as%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcomfortable-with-discomfort-of-change-full-text-of-gautam-adanis-speech-7142750%5C%22%3EAdani%20also%20shared%20the%20%26quot%3Bpriceless%20lessons%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20trading%20taught%20him%3A%20%26quot%3B...trading%20makes%20a%20great%20teacher.%20What%20I%20learned%2C%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20was%20that%20trading%20does%20not%20come%20with%20safety%20nets.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20a%20discipline%20where%20you%20must%20find%20the%20courage%20to%20fly%20without%20any%20protective%20nets.%20You%20must%20learn%20to%20take%20the%20jump%20and%20trust%20your%20own%20wings.%20In%20this%20field%2C%20hesitation%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20winning%20and%20losing.%20Each%20decision%20is%20a%20test%2C%20not%20just%20against%20the%20market%2C%20but%20against%20the%20limits%20of%20your%20own%20mind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToo%20much%20of%20an%20attachment%20to%20outcomes%20limits%20your%20ability%20to%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20another%20lesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asserted%20that%20the%20Adani%20Group%20stands%20where%20it%20is%20today%20because%20it%20is%20not%20afraid%20to%20challenge%20itself.%20%26quot%3BTo%20accept%20the%20status%20quo%20is%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20destiny%20where%20you%20stop%20questioning%2C%20stop%20dreaming%2C%20and%20stop%20exploring%20your%20own%20potential...%20We%20continuously%20redefined%20our%20boundaries%2C%20refused%20to%20accept%20limits%2C%20and%20were%20comfortable%20with%20the%20discomfort%20of%20change.%20Our%20journey%20has%20been%20built%20on%20the%20foundation%20of%20grit%2C%20and%20a%20relentless%20drive%20to%20overcome%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20speech%2C%20Mr%20Adani%20also%20spotlighted%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fevery-attack-makes-us-stronger-gautam-adani-responds-to-us-allegations-7142550%5C%22%3Echallenges%20faced%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20mentioned%20the%20report%20by%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20in%20January%202023%20and%20a%20legal%20matter%20involving%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20attack%20makes%20us%20stronger%20and%20every%20obstacle%20becomes%20a%20stepping%20stone%20for%20a%20more%20resilient%20