ide.%20The%20Test%20team%20then%20thrashed%20Bangladesh%202-0%20before%20a%20nightmare%20outing%20against%20New%20Zealand%20put%20Gambhir%20under%20massive%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20are%20being%20unfair%20to%20him...%20If%20you%20will%20start%20judging%20people%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20coaching%20role%20or%20whatever%20way%20it%20is%20being%20looked%20at%2C%20it%20is%20too%20short%20a%20time%20to%20for%20people%20to%20be%20judged%2C%26quot%3B%20Jadeja%20told%20PTI%20Videos%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20FICCI%20Turf%20event%20on%20Saturday..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20not%20convinced%20that%20he%20is%20good%2C%20then%20one%20performance%20here%20or%20there%20will%20be%20able%20to%20convince%20anyone.%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20is%20the%20time%20to%20judge%20him%2C%20it%20is%20the%20time%20we%20should%20enjoy%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Jadeja%2C%20known%20for%20his%20exploits%20in%20the%2050-over%20game%20where%20he%20scored%20over%205000%20runs%20in%20196%20ODIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20massive%20295-run%20win%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%20first%20Border-Gavaskar%20Test%20at%20Perth%20following%20the%20no-show%20against%20the%20Kiwis%20has%20come%20as%20a%20huge%20morale-booster%20for%20the%20side%20and%20Jadeja%20felt%20Gambhir%20should%20not%20be%20judged%20within%20six%20months%20of%20his%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20there%20are%20phases%20and%20it%20will%20come%2C%20sometimes%20you%20win%20and%20sometimes%20you%20lose.%20So%2C%20I%20won't%20go%20into%20that%20direction%20and%20start%20judging%20him%20(Gambhir)%20in%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20knew%20what%20you%20were%20asking%20for%20and%20what%20you%20were%20getting.%20He%20is%20a%20very%20clear-cut%20person%20and%20he%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20throughout%20his%20life.%20So%2C%20what%20your%20are%20seeing%20now%20is%20what%20everyone%20expected%20of%20him%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%20Jadeja%20said%20that%20regular%20Test%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20return%20for%20the%20second%20Test%20at%20Adelaide%20from%20December%206%20after%20missing%20the%20opening%20game%20will%20boost%20India's%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHim%20(Rohit%20Sharma)%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20team%20will%20surely%20boost%20India's%20confidence%2C%20for%20sure.%20He%20is%20a%20leader%2C%20when%20the%20chips%20were%20down%2C%20team%20was%20going%20down%2C%20he%20stood%20up%20there%20as%20the%20leader%20and%20now%20when%20the%20team%20is%20going%20up%2C%20he%20will%20be%20again%20there%20as%20the%20leader.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20KL%20Rahul%20and%20Rohit%20should%20swap%20batting%20slots%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20after%20the%20former%20had%20a%20formidable%20outing%20in%20the%20Perth%20game%2C%20Jadeja%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20details%20of%20what%20the%20team%20is%20thinking%20right%20now%2C%20no%20views%20on%20who%20should%20bat%20at%20what%20number.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20always%20been%20an%20asset%20to%20the%20side%20wherever%20he%20bats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpening%20the%20innings%20with%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Rahul%20scored%2077%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20at%20Perth%2C%20helping%20India%20to%20set%20a%20massive%20534-run%20target.%20Some%20experts%20have%20opined%20that%20Rahul%20should%20open%20in%20the%20Adelaide%20Test%20as%20well%2C%20while%20Rohit%20should%20in%20at%20one-down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732982160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fpris5qqg_gautam-gambhir-_625x300_15_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhirs-coaching-record-receives-big-verdict-from-ex-india-star-unfair-7140236%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ajay%20Jadeja%20defended%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20from%20the%20criticism%20he%20has%20received%20following%20the%200-3%20drubbing%20against%20Ne