eech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBillionare%20Gautam%20Adani%20today%20addressed%20the%2051st%20India%20Gem%20%26amp%3B%20Jewellery%20Awards%20in%20Jaipur.%20During%20his%20speech%2C%20Mr%20Adani%20responded%20to%20the%20legal%20matter%20involving%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice.%20He%20also%20spoke%20about%20how%20he%20made%20his%20first%20commission%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20his%20full%20speech%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20an%20honour%20to%20stand%20before%20you%20today%20at%20the%2051st%20India%20Gem%20%26amp%3B%20Jewellery%20Awards.%20This%20is%20a%20celebration%20of%20India's%20remarkable%20heritage%20in%20craftsmanship%20and%20innovation.%20My%20sincere%20congratulations%20to%20all%20the%20awardees%20whose%20exceptional%20efforts%20have%20carried%20forward%20India's%20rich%20legacy%20in%20jewellery.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20centuries%2C%20India%20has%20been%20recognized%20as%20the%20undisputed%20leader%20in%20the%20space%20of%20gemstones%20and%20as%20the%20nation%20of%20unmatched%20artisans.%20Jewellery%20in%20our%20culture%20is%20not%20just%20ornamental%20-%20it%20is%20deeply%20symbolic%2C%20a%20marker%20of%20heritage%2C%20emotion%2C%20and%20aspiration.%20Your%20work%20has%20kept%20this%20tradition%20alive%20and%20relevant%20in%20an%20ever-changing%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20industry%20is%20a%20powerhouse%2C%20providing%20employment%20to%20over%20five%20million%20Indians%20-%20a%20figure%20comparable%20to%20the%20workforce%20of%20our%20IT%20sector.%20Surat%2C%20as%20the%20global%20epicentre%20of%20diamond%20cutting%20and%20polishing%2C%20employs%20over%20a%20million%20skilled%20workers.%20This%20industry%20is%20not%20just%20an%20economic%20driver%3B%20it%20is%20a%20source%20of%20pride%20for%20our%20nation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHowever%2C%20with%20great%20success%20comes%20an%20even%20greater%20responsibility%3A%20to%20innovate%2C%20expand%2C%20and%20lead%20courageously%20in%20the%20face%20of%20disruption.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20dear%20friends%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20the%20jewel%20in%20the%20global%20crown%20of%20the%20cut-and-polished%20diamond%20market%2C%20holding%2026.5%25%20of%20the%20share%2C%20and%20silver%20jewellery%20at%2030%25.%20But%20the%20recent%2014%25%20decline%20in%20exports%20is%20more%20than%20a%20statistic%20-%20it%20is%20a%20wake-up%20call.%20It%20signals%20a%20turning%20point%20where%20challenges%2C%20both%20temporary%20and%20permanent%2C%20demand%20that%20we%20reimagine%20our%20approach.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20at%20the%20start%20of%20a%20revolution.%20Sustainability%20and%20technology%20-%20two%20forces%20reshaping%20industries%20worldwide%20-%20are%20now%20at%20our%20doorstep.%20The%20rise%20of%20lab-grown%20diamonds%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20transparency%20and%20ethical%20practices%2C%20shifting%20consumer%20priorities%2C%20and%20the%20digital%20wave%20are%20not%20just%20disrupting%20the%20status%20quo%3B%20they%20are%20creating%20a%20new%20blueprint%20necessary%20for%20success.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20therefore%20our%20moment%20to%20lead.%20The%20industry%20must%20think%20differently%2C%20act%20urgently%2C%20and%20innovate%20courageously.%20Today's%20inflection%20point%20must%20be%20turned%20into%20an%20era%20of%20unprecedented%20opportunity%20for%20growth.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20dear%20friends%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAllow%20me%20to%20narrate%20a%20story%20to%20set%20some%20context.%20Over%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20during%20a%20trip%20to%20California%2C%20I%20saw%20my%20first%20lab-grown%20diamond.%20The%20founder%20had%20enthusiastically%20shared%20his%20vision%2C%20confident%20this%20was%20the%20start%20of%20a%20revolution%20in%20the%20jewellery%20industry.%20And%20he%20was%20right.%20As%20we%20now%20know%2C%20lab-grown%20diamonds%20have%20evolved%20from%20a%20scientific%20wonder%20to%20a%20market%20disruptor.%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20officially%20recognized%20by%20the%20US%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20as%20real%20diamonds.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThese%20diamonds%20now%20cost%20significantly%20less%20than%20the%20natural%20diamonds.%20Advances%20in%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20and%20material%20science%20are%20pushing%20their%20quality%20and%20precision%20even%20further.%20It's%20not%20far-fetched%20to%20imagine%20a%20future%20where%20we%20design%20our%20own%20diamonds%20-%20specifying%20every%20detail%2C%20from%20cut%20to%20colour%2C%20clarity%2C%20and%20carat%20weight%20-%20making%20each%20piece%20uniquely%20personal.%20This%20is%20the%20future%20we%20must%20embrace.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAlso%2C%20beyond%20traditional%20gems%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20jewellery%20itself%20is%20shifting.%20Watches%2C%20smartphones%2C%20and%20wearables%20are%20becoming%20the%20new%20personal%20status%20symbols%2C%20redefining%20luxury.%20Younger%20generations%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20are%20preferring%20technology%20and%20experiences%20over%20conventional%20luxury%20goods.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnother%20trend%20reshaping%20the%20market%20is%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20unique%2C%20customized%20pieces%2C%20sparking%20a%20rise%20in%20custom%20design%20services.%20With%20technologies%20like%203D%20printing%2C%20CAD%20software%2C%20Virtual%20Reality%2C%20and%20Augmented%20Reality%2C%20the%20process%20of%20designing%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20experiencing%20jewellery%20is%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20transformation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThese%20trends%20force%20us%20to%20rethink%20what%20we%20produce.%20They%20challenge%20us%20to%20create%20deeper%20emotional%20and%20traditional%20connections%20in%20line%20with%20changing%20consumer%20needs%20and%20behaviours.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20is%20this%20spirit%20of%20transformation%20that%20I%20want%20to%20explore%20today%20-%20what%20it%20truly%20means%20to%20Break%20the%20Status%20Quo.%20Only%20by%20challenging%20the%20status%20quo%20can%20we%20unlock%20new%20opportunities%20and%20shape%20the%20future.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20dear%20friends%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELet%20me%20start%20with%20a%20personal%20story%20about%20the%20first%20time%20that%20I%20broke%20the%20status%20quo.%20This%20story%20holds%20a%20very%20special%20place%20in%20my%20heart.%20It%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20who%20I%20was%20to%20become.%20Diamond%20trading%20was%20my%20entry%20point%20into%20the%20journey%20I%20took%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20year%201978%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2016%2C%20I%20left%20my%20school%2C%20left%20my%20home%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20and%20took%20a%20one-way%20ticket%20to%20Mumbai.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20I%20would%20do%20but%20I%20was%20clear%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20entrepreneur.%20And%20I%20believed%20Mumbai%20was%20the%20city%20of%20opportunities%20that%20would%20give%20me%20this%20chance.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20got%20my%20first%20opportunity%20at%20Mahendra%20Brothers%2C%20where%20I%20learned%20the%20art%20of%20diamond%20assorting.%20Even%20today%2C%20I%20recall%20the%20joy%20of%20closing%20my%20first%20deal.%20It%20was%20a%20transaction%20with%20a%20Japanese%20buyer%20and%20I%20got%20a%20commission%20of%2010%2C000%20rupees.%20That%20day%20marked%20the%20start%20of%20a%20journey%20that%20would%20shape%20the%20way%20I%20would%20live%20my%20life%20as%20an%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20also%20learned%20that%20trading%20makes%20a%20great%20teacher.%20What%20I%20learned%2C%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20was%20that%20trading%20does%20not%20come%20with%20safety%20nets.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20a%20discipline%20where%20you%20must%20find%20the%20courage%20to%20fly%20without%20any%20protective%20nets.%20You%20must%20learn%20to%20take%20the%20jump%20and%20trust%20your%20own%20wings.%20In%20this%20field%2C%20hesitation%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20winning%20and%20losing.%20Each%20decision%20is%20a%20test%2C%20not%20just%20against%20the%20market%2C%20but%20against%20the%20limits%20of%20your%20own%20mind.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrading%20also%20taught%20me%20another%20priceless%20lesson.%20Too%20much%20of%20an%20attachment%20to%20outcomes%20limits%20your%20ability%20to%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETherefore%2C%20my%20dear%20friends%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20accept%20the%20status%20quo%20is%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20destiny%20where%20you%20stop%20questioning%2C%20stop%20dreaming%2C%20and%20stop%20exploring%20your%20own%20potential.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20stands%20where%20it%20is%20today%20because%20we%20are%20not%20afraid%20to%20challenge%20ourselves.%20We%20continuously%20redefined%20our%20boundaries%2C%20refused%20to%20accept%20limits%2C%20and%20were%20comfortable%20with%20the%20discomfort%20of%20change.%20Our%20journey%20has%20been%20built%20on%20the%20foundation%20of%20grit%2C%20and%20a%20relentless%20drive%20to%20overcome%20challenges.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20I%20got%20to%20Mumbai%20when%20I%20was%2016.%20But%2C%20in%201981%2C%20just%20as%20I%20turned%2019%2C%20I%20was%20called%20back%20to%20Ahmedabad%20to%20help%20with%20my%20family's%20polymer%20business.%20India%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20faced%20a%20great%20shortage%20of%20raw%20materials%20given%20the%20intense%20import%20controls.%20I%20saw%2C%20first%20hand%2C%20the%20struggles%20that%20every%20small-scale%20industry%20faced.%20And%20then%2C%20it%20was%20in%201985%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Shri%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20that%20India%20began%20to%20take%20its%20first%20steps%20towards%20economic%20liberalization.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20saw%20an%20early%20opportunity%20in%20these%20changes%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20relaxation%20of%20import%20policies%20for%20industries%20facing%20raw%20material%20shortages.%20While%20I%20had%20no%20prior%20experience%20in%20trading%20polymers%2C%20I%20still%20took%20a%20calculated%20risk%20and%20established%20a%20trading%20organization%20focused%20on%20imports.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBy%201990%2C%20my%20trading%20venture%20was%20performing%20well%2C%20but%20then%20India%20itself%20faced%20a%20critical%20moment.%20The%20massive%20foreign%20exchange%20crisis%20of%201991%20threatened%20the%20entire%20economy%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20a%20wave%20of%20economic%20reforms%20initiated%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20and%20then%20Finance%20Minister%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThese%20reforms%20dismantled%20the%20License%20Raj%2C%20opened%20up%20the%20economy%20to%20foreign%20investments%2C%20and%20reduced%20import%20tariffs.%20I%20saw%2C%20in%20this%20transformation%20of%20the%20Indian%20business%20landscape%20an%20opportunity%20to%20scale%20further.%20In%201991%20itself%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2029%2C%20I%20established%20a%20global%20trading%20house%2C%20expanding%20into%20polymers%2C%20metals%2C%20textiles%2C%20and%20agricultural%20products.%20In%20just%20two%20years%2C%20we%20became%20India's%20largest%20global%20trading%20house%2C%20proving%20that%20the%20combination%20of%20speed%20and%20scale%20is%20a%20powerful%20driver%20of%20growth.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHowever%2C%20while%20the%20import-export%20business%20did%20very%20well%2C%20I%20had%20started%20questioning%20the%20status%20quo.%20I%20began%20realizing%20that%20for%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20growth%20I%20would%20need%20to%20own%20assets%20and%20build%20something%20lasting.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20I%20had%20to%20challenge%20everything%20I%20knew.%20Remember%2C%20I%20had%20no%20experience%20in%20building%20anything.%20We%20had%20not%20even%20laid%20a%20single%20brick%20in%20our%20life.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBut%20opportunities%20show%20up%20for%20those%20that%20seek.%20And%20it%20was%20in%201995%20that%20a%20transformative%20opportunity%20emerged%20when%20the%20BJP-led%20Gujarat%20government%20announced%20its%20port-led%20industrial%20development%20plan%20under%20a%20Public-Private-%20Partnership%20mode.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20summarize%20a%20long%20story%2C%20we%20quickly%20moved%20to%20establish%20Mundra%20Port.%20This%20transition%2C%20about%2030%20years%20back%2C%20was%20the%20start%20of%20our%20journey%20into%20the%20domain%20of%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20dear%20friends%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20tell%20my%20team%20all%20the%20time%20that%20the%20future%20belongs%20to%20those%20who%20dare%20to%20see%20beyond%20the%20present%20and%20who%20recognize%20that%20today's%20limits%20are%20tomorrow's%20starting%20points.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETherefore%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EBe%20it%20my%20leaving%20home%20to%20bet%20on%20myself%20as%20a%20young%20diamond%20trader%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3Eor%20believing%20that%20we%20could%20build%20the%20nation's%20largest%20port%20against%20the%20advice%20of%20all%20experts%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3Eto%20laying%20India's%20first%20private%20railway%20to%20connect%20Mundra%20Port%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3Eto%20being%20able%20to%20establish%20the%20world's%20largest%20single-site%20thermal%20power%20generation%20capacity%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3Eto%20building%20the%20world's%20largest%20coal%20import%20terminal%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3Eto%20being%20the%20first%20in%20India%20to%20build%20a%20private%20HVDC%20line%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3Eto%20making%20India's%20largest%20ever%20investment%20in%20an%20OECD%20country%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3Eto%20operating%20India's%20largest%20network%20of%20airports%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3Eto%20investing%20in%20a%20port%20in%20Israel%20and%20making%20a%20bet%20on%20the%20future%20of%20the%20India%20-%20Middle%20East%20corridor%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3Eto%20the%20redevelopment%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20slum%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E-%20as%20we%20took%20these%20journeys%20going%20beyond%20our%20comfort%20zone%2C%20we%20discovered%20other%20new%20possibilities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHad%20we%20remained%20satisfied%20with%20the%20status%20quo%2C%20these%20new%20and%20adjacent%20opportunities%20would%20have%20never%20come%20our%20way.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELet%20me%20now%20outline%20a%20few%20examples.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20logistics%2C%20what%20started%20as%20a%20port%20jetty%2C%20to%20import%20coal%20in%201998%2C%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20become%20the%20country's%20largest%20port%20business.%20This%20business%20today%20-%20spans%20a%20network%20of%2015%20national%20and%205%20international%20ports%20and%20thereby%20allowing%20us%20to%20expand%20into%20building%20a%20network%20of%20integrated%20logistic%20nodes.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThese%20nodes%20now%20are%20made%20up%20of%20ports%2C%20rail%2C%20highways%2C%20warehouses%2C%20inland%20container%20depots%2C%20fulfilment%20centres%2C%20and%20trucking%20in%20a%20way%20no%20other%20company%20has%20ever%20achieved%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20journey%20has%20taken%20us%20deep%20into%20the%20Middle%20East%20-%20all%20the%20way%20into%20the%20Mediterranean%20through%20Israel%20-%20and%20into%20the%20heart%20of%20Africa.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20is%20no%20more%20just%20about%20ports.%20It%20is%20now%20about%20leveraging%20India's%20geographic%20location%20and%20doing%20our%20part%20to%20help%20make%20our%20nation%20become%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20logistics%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELikewise%2C%20what%20started%20as%20a%20single%20power%20plant%20in%202007%2C%20has%20now%20become%20not%20just%20India's%20largest%20private%20thermal%20power%20generation%20company%20but%20has%20also%20allowed%20us%20to%20expand%20into%20adjacencies.%20This%20expansion%20has%20seen%20us%20become%20India's%20largest%20private%20transmission%20company%2C%20largest%20private%20power%20distribution%20company%2C%20largest%20mine%20developer%20and%20operator%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20only%20company%20that%20successfully%20took%20up%20the%20challenge%20of%20cross-border%20supply%20of%20power%20to%20help%20a%20neighbouring%20nation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20move%20into%20the%20area%20of%20renewable%20energy.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20India's%20largest%20solar%20panel%20manufacturing%20company%20as%20well%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20single-site%20renewable%20energy%20facility%2C%20well%20on%20our%20way%20to%20generate%2030%20GW%20of%20power%2C%20spread%20over%20a%20massive%20single%20span%20of%20land%20of%20more%20than%20500%20square%20kilometres.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYet%20another%20example%20of%20challenging%20the%20status%20quo%20is%20our%20move%20into%20the%20airport%20business.%20In%20less%20than%20three%20years%2C%20we%20became%20the%20largest%20airport%20operator%20in%20the%20country.%20We%20then%20built%20our%20adjacencies%20that%20made%20us%20the%20largest%20airport%20logistics%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Eplayer%20with%20almost%2040%25%20of%20India's%20air%20cargo%20and%20have%20now%20undertaken%20the%20world's%20largest%20slum%20redevelopment%20initiative%2C%20the%20Dharavi%20project.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnd%2C%20I%20must%20add%20here%20that%2C%20for%20me%2C%20Dharavi%20is%20not%20just%20about%20slum%20redevelopment.%20It%20is%20about%20restoring%20dignity%2C%20creating%20a%20sustainable%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20changing%20the%20status%20quo%20for%20over%20one%20million%20residents.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20dear%20friends%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELooking%20back%2C%20while%20we%20have%20had%20our%20successes%2C%20our%20challenges%20have%20been%20even%20bigger.%20However%2C%20these%20challenges%20have%20not%20broken%20us.%20Instead%2C%20they%20have%20defined%20us.%20They%20have%20made%20us%20tougher%20and%20give%20us%20the%20unshakeable%20belief%20that%20after%20every%20fall%2C%20we%20will%20rise%20again%2C%20stronger%2C%20and%20more%20resilient%20than%20before.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELet%20me%20talk%20about%20three%20examples.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFirst%20-%20In%202010%2C%20when%20we%20were%20investing%20in%20a%20coal%20mine%20in%20Australia%2C%20our%20objective%20was%20clear%3A%20How%20to%20make%20India%20energy%20secure%20-%20and%20replace%20every%20two%20tons%20of%20poor-quality%20Indian%20coal%20with%20one%20ton%20of%20high-quality%20coal%20from%20Australia%3F%20However%2C%20the%20resistance%20from%20NGOs%20was%20huge%20and%20lasted%20almost%20a%20decade.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20so%20intense%20that%20we%20ended%20up%20funding%20the%20entire%20project%20of%2010%20billion%20dollars%20with%20our%20own%20equity.%20While%20we%20now%20have%20a%20world%20class%20operating%20mine%20in%20Australia%20and%20it%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20great%20sign%20of%20our%20resilience%2C%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20100%25%20equity%20funding%20took%20away%20over%2030%20billion%20dollars%20of%20debt%20financing%20from%20our%20green%20energy%20projects.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20next%20example%20is%20from%20January%20last%20year%2C%20just%20as%20we%20were%20getting%20ready%20to%20launch%20our%20Follow-on%20Public%20Offering.%20We%20faced%20a%20short-selling%20attack%20initiated%20from%20abroad.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20typical%20financial%20strike%3B%20it%20was%20a%20double%20hit%20-%20targeting%20our%20financial%20stability%20and%20pulling%20us%20into%20a%20political%20controversy.%20All%20of%20this%20was%20further%20amplified%20by%20certain%20media%20with%20vested%20interests.%20But%20even%20in%20the%20face%20of%20such%20adversity%2C%20our%20commitment%20to%20our%20principles%20remained%20strong.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAfter%20successfully%20raising%2020%2C000%20crore%20rupees%20from%20India's%20largest-ever%20FPO%2C%20we%20made%20the%20extraordinary%20decision%20to%20return%20the%20proceeds.%20We%20then%20further%20demonstrated%20our%20resilience%20by%20raising%20capital%20from%20several%20international%20sources%20and%20proactively%20reducing%20our%20Debt%20to%20EBITDA%20ratio%20to%20below%202.5%20times%2C%20an%20unmatched%20metric%20in%20the%20global%20infrastructure%20space.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMoreover%2C%20our%20all-time%20record%20financial%20results%20in%20the%20same%20year%20showcased%20our%20commitment%20to%20operational%20excellence.%20Not%20a%20single%20Indian%20or%20foreign%20credit%20rating%20agency%20downgraded%20us.%20Finally%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India's%20affirmation%20of%20our%20actions%20validated%20our%20approach.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20third%20example%20is%20very%20recent.%20As%20most%20of%20you%20would%20have%20read%2C%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20back%2C%20we%20faced%20a%20set%20of%20allegations%20from%20the%20US%20about%20compliance%20practices%20at%20Adani%20Green%20Energy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20we%20have%20faced%20such%20challenges.%20What%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20is%20that%20every%20attack%20makes%20us%20stronger%20and%20every%20obstacle%20becomes%20a%20stepping%20stone%20for%20a%20more%20resilient%20Adani%20Group.%20The%20fact%20is%20that%20despite%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20vested%20reporting%2C%20no%20