quot%3BThe%20fact%20is%20that%20despite%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20vested%20reporting%2C%20no%20one%20from%20the%20Adani%20side%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20any%20violation%20of%20the%20FCPA%20or%20any%20conspiracy%20to%20obstruct%20justice.%20Yet%2C%20in%20today's%20world%2C%20negativity%20spreads%20faster%20than%20facts%20-%20and%20as%20we%20work%20through%20the%20legal%20process%2C%20I%20want%20to%20reconfirm%20our%20absolute%20commitment%20to%20world%20class%20regulatory%20compliance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20gathering%20that%20despite%20the%20successes%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20the%20challenges%20it%20has%20faced%20were%20even%20bigger.%20%26quot%3BThese%20challenges%20have%20not%20broken%20us.%20Instead%2C%20they%20have%20defined%20us.%20They%20have%20made%20us%20tougher%20and%20give%20us%20the%20unshakeable%20belief%20that%20after%20every%20fall%2C%20we%20will%20rise%20again%2C%20stronger%2C%20and%20more%20resilient%20than%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20the%20attack%20by%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20in%20January%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Just%20as%20we%20were%20getting%20ready%20to%20launch%20our%20follow-on%20public%20offering%20(FPO)%2C%20we%20faced%20a%20short-selling%20attack%20initiated%20from%20abroad.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20typical%20financial%20strike%3B%20it%20was%20a%20double%20hit%20-%20targeting%20our%20financial%20stability%20and%20pulling%20us%20into%20a%20political%20controversy.%20All%20of%20this%20was%20further%20amplified%20by%20certain%20media%20with%20vested%20interests.%20But%20even%20in%20the%20face%20of%20such%20adversity%2C%20our%20commitment%20to%20our%20principles%20remained%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20successfully%20raising%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20from%20India's%20largest-ever%20FPO%2C%20we%20made%20the%20extraordinary%20decision%20to%20return%20the%20proceeds.%20We%20then%20further%20demonstrated%20our%20resilience%20by%20raising%20capital%20from%20several%20international%20sources%20and%20proactively%20reducing%20our%20debt%20to%20EBITDA%20ratio%20to%20below%202.5%20times%2C%20an%20unmatched%20metric%20in%20the%20global%20infrastructure%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoreover%2C%20our%20all-time%20record%20financial%20results%20in%20the%20same%20year%20showcased%20our%20commitment%20to%20operational%20excellence.%20Not%20a%20single%20Indian%20or%20foreign%20credit%20rating%20agency%20downgraded%20us.%20Finally%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India's%20affirmation%20of%20our%20actions%20validated%20our%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20Adani%2C%20his%20nephew%20Sagar%20Adani%2C%20and%20senior%20executive%20Vneet%20Jaain%20are%20clear%20of%20any%20bribery%20charges%20per%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Green%2C%20a%20firm%20under%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20had%20also%20called%20media%20reports%20on%20the%20US%20legal%20matter%20as%20%26quot%3Bincorrect%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20a%20stock%20exchange%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20includes%20five%20counts%2C%20but%20the%20first%20and%20fifth%20counts%20-%20conspiracy%20to%20violate%20the%20FCPA%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20obstruct%20justice%20-%20do%20not%20mention%20the%20three%20directors%2C%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Sagar%20Adani%2C%20and%20Vneet%20Jaain%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20statement%20said%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bflawed%20understanding%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20US%20indictment%20by%20various%20media%2C%20foreign%20as%20well%20as%20Indian%2C%20has%20led%20to%20%26quot%3Bincorrect%20and%20reckless%20reporting%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20three%20Adani%20Group%20directors%20faced%20corruption%20and%20bribery%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20indictment