0chocolate%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20the%20dairy%2C%20Dunkin'%20hot%20chocolate%20was%20noticeably%20less%20creamy%2C%20though%20it%20had%20an%20intense%20chocolate%20flavor%20%E2%80%94%20a%20likely%20benefit%20of%20the%20mocha%20syrup%20on%20top.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EKrispy%20Kreme%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Krispy%20Kreme%20cup%20being%20held%20up%20by%20a%20woman's%20hand%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Krispy%20Kreme%20storefront.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653f08c796f7540cd068d3a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHot%20cocoa%20from%20Krispy%20Kreme%20was%20the%20least%20expensive%20among%20the%20five%20national%20chains%2C%20and%20the%20second%20best%20in%20overall%20flavor.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20chain%20I%20rarely%20visit%2C%20Krispy%20Kreme%20surprised%20me%20by%20coming%20in%20second%20place%20for%20its%20overall%20flavor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%243.55%2C%20the%20doughnut%20chain's%20midsize%20cocoa%20was%20less%20expensive%20than%20the%20other%20major%20hot%20chocolate%20movers%2C%20but%20it%20rose%20above%20almost%20all%20of%20them%20by%20using%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghirardelli-chocolate-in-san-francisco-2016-11%5C%22%3E%20Ghirardelli%3C%2Fa%3E%20powder%20base%20with%20steamed%202%25%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20served%20warm%2C%20not%20hot%2C%20and%20included%20whipped%20cream%20but%20not%20sprinkles%20or%20drizzle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-krispy-kreme-doughnuts-iconic-glazed-ipo-stock-filing-2021-6%5C%22%3EKrispy%20Kreme%3C%2Fa%3E's%20cocoa%20had%20no%20frills%2C%20but%20offered%20more%20nuanced%20flavor%20than%20Peet's%2C%20Dunkin'%2C%20and%20The%20Coffee%20Bean%20%26amp%3B%20Tea%20Leaf%20without%20having%20quite