th%20house-made%20mocha%20syrup%2C%20then%20topped%20with%20whipped%20cream.%20Though%20notably%20missing%20any%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-add-to-hot-chocolate-2018-12%5C%22%3E%20unique%20toppings%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20a%20chocolate%20syrup%20swirl%20or%20marshmallow%2C%20which%20would%20undoubtedly%20heighten%20the%20experience%2C%20this%20hot%20chocolate%20was%20rich%20and%20creamy%20without%20being%20too%20sweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drink%20had%20some%20back-end%20bitter%20notes%20that%20I%20could%20see%20making%20my%20opinion%20controversial%2C%20but%20having%20a%20more%20complex%20flavor%20made%20Starbucks'%20hot%20cocoa%20more%20enjoyable%20than%20the%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20This%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20November%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-fast-food-hot-chocolate-coffee-chains-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732975917000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653f075d356802a56be6fba7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-fast-food-hot-chocolate-coffee-chains-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20find%20the%20best%20fast-food%20hot%20cocoa%20from%20coffee%20chains%2C%20I%20tried%20Starbucks%2C%20Peet's%20Coffee%2C%20Coffee%20Bean%20%26amp%3B%20Tea%20Leaf%2C%20Dunkin'%2C%20and%20Krispy%20Kreme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-fast-food-hot-chocolate-coffee-chains-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20must%20strengthen%20national%2C%20int'l%20collaboration%20in%20research%3A%20Mukesh%20Ambani%2