er%20dollar%20boosts%20consumers'%20purchasing%20power%20and%20can%20even%20help%20lower%20inflation%2C%20but%20it%20hurts%20US%20exports.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%20firms%20face%20profit%20headwinds%20due%20to%20currency%20conversion%20challenges%2C%20which%20could%20ding%20stock%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dollar%20has%20soared%20since%20Donald%20Trump's%20election%20win%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20and%20a%20stronger%20US%20currency%20can%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20consumers'%20wallets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dollar%20index%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20US%20dollar%20against%20a%20basket%20of%20currencies%2C%20has%20surged%20as%20much%20as%205%25%20since%20Trump's%20win%20and%20is%20up%20as%20much%20as%208%25%20since%20October%201%2C%20trading%20at%20its%20highest%20level%20in%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dollar%20has%20gained%20on%20expectations%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fdonald-trump-tariffs-mexico-canadan-china-dollar-peso-oil-stocks-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20policies%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20potentially%20stoke%20inflation%2C%20which%20would%20force%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20to%20keep%20interest%20rates%20elevated%20to%20counteract%20higher%20prices.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigher%20rates%20spur%20greater%20demand%20for%20dollars%20from%20overseas%20investors%2C%20who%20invest%20them%20into%20higher-yielding%20US%20assets%20like%20Treasurys%20and%20other%20debt%20securities.%20Higher%20interest%20rates%20also%20lower%20the%20overall%20supply%20of%20dollars%20in%20the%20system%20by%20discouraging%20borrowing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20a%20stronger%20US%20dollar%20can%20impact%20consumers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228df9c32d-c277-4aae-96f7-34533a03e98c%5C%22%3EConsider%20a%20foreign%20vacation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20stronger%20US%20dollar%20ultimately%20means%20that%20your%20greenbacks%20have%20more%20purchasing%20power%20when%20paying%20for%20goods%20and%20services%20priced%20in%20other%20currencies.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20especially%20felt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhen%20traveling%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20dealing%20with%20exchange%20rates.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20stronger%20dollar%20means%20that%20when%20you%20convert%20money%20into%20pesos%2C%20euros%2C%20or%20yen%2C%20you%20ultimately%20receive%20more%20of%20the%20foreign%20currency%20than%20you%20would%20under%20a%20weak%20dollar%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20stronger%20dollar%20may%20help%20you%20feel%20like%20a%20free-spending%20prince%20with%20a%20hefty%20traveling%20budget%20while%20on%20an%20overseas%20vacation%20as%20the%20value%20of%20your%20dollar%20will%20go%20a%20lot%20further%20when%20converted%20to%20local%20currency%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20enjoy%20upgrades%20to%20your%20lodging%2C%20food%2C%20entertainment%2C%20and%20excursions%2C%26quot%3B%20Sam%20Stovall%2C%20chief%20investment%20strategist%20at%20CFRA%20Research%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8ce76a6-65f3-4a2c-9acd-50ba63aafe62%5C%22%3EGet%20more%20'bang%20for%20your%20buck'%20buying%20foreign%20goods%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20even%20need%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20to%20benefit%20from%20a%20stronger%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rob%20Haworth%2C%20senior%20investment%20strategist%20at%20US%20Bank%20Wealth%20Management%2C%20foreign%20goods%20bought%20with%20a%20stronger%20dollar%20are%20typically%20%26quot%3Bless%20costly%20given%20the%20rising%20purchasing%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20even%20possible%20that%20a%20stronger%20dollar%20could%20help%20lower%20domestic%20inflation%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20short%20term.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20near%20term%2C%20US%20dollar%20strength%20is%20pressing%20down%20on%20inflation%20and%20commodity%20prices%20in%20particular%2C%26quot%3B%20Haworth%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThe%20stronger%20US%20dollar%20makes%20dollar-priced%20commodities%20more%20expensive%20for%20foreign%20buyers%2C%20hurting%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20lower%20demand%20ultimately%20means%20lower%20prices%20if%20supply%20is%20steady.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20a%20barrel%20of%20WTI%20crude%20oil%20is%20down%2013%25%20since%20it%20peaked%20at%20about%20%2478%20in%20early%20October.%20Other%20commodities%20like%20gasoline%2C%20copper%2C%20and%20soybeans%2C%20all%20key%20inputs%20for%20various%20goods%2C%20have%20moved%20lower%20since%20the%20dollar%20surge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForeign%20companies%20that%20export%20their%20goods%20to%20the%20US%20also%20have%20room%20to%20lower%20their%20prices%2C%20which%20could%20ultimately%20result%20in%20lower%20costs%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20a%20strengthening%20dollar%20those%20countries%20experiencing%20a%20weaker%20local%20currency%20versus%20the%20USD%20will%20have%20a%20competitive%20advantage%20exporting%20to%20the%20US.%20We%20can%20buy%20their%20products%20for%20less%20than%20before%20solely%20due%20to%20the%20USD%20appreciation%2C%26quot%3B%20Arthur%20Laffer%20Jr.%2C%20president%20at%20Laffer%20Tengler%20Investments%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStovall%20echoed%20those%20comments%2C%20saying%20consumers%20should%20%26quot%3Bget%20more%20bang%20for%20your%20buck%26quot%3B%20when%20purchasing%20everyday%20items%20made%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222dd63a7d-ff38-459f-810a-622384a5022a%5C%22%3EA%20strong%20dollar%20might%20not%20be%20great%20news%20for%20your%20investment%20portfolio%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20strong%20US%20dollar%20could%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20consumers'%20wallets%20when%20traveling%20abroad%20or%20buying%20foreign%20goods%2C%20it%20could%20be%20detrimental%20to%20investment%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20especially%20true%20for%20US-based%20companies%20that%20generate%20revenues%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultinational%20companies%20sell%20their%20goods%20or%20services%20overseas%20in%20the%20country's%20local%20currency%20and%20then%20convert%20those%20profits%20into%20US%20dollars%20when%20reporting%20earnings.%20But%20if%20the%20dollar%20is%20strong%20and%20the%20local%20currency%20is%20weak%2C%20then%20they'll%20ultimately%20see%20weaker%20profits%20when%20converting%20the%20foreign%20currency%20into%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20lower%20profitability%20will%20weigh%20on%20stock%20prices.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20especially%20painful%20for%20US%20companies%20that%20produce%20their%20goods%20in%20America%20and%20then%20ship%20them%20overseas%2C%20as%20they%20likely%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20input%20costs%20with%20a%20strong%20US%20dollar%2C%20sell%20them%20overseas%20in%20the%20weaker%20local%20currency%2C%20and%20then%20convert%20that%20currency%20back%20to%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20USD%20is%20getting%20stronger%2C%20US%20exports%20to%20those%20countries%20will%20be%20more%20expensive%20on%20a%20relative%20basis%20than%20before%20the%20currency%20appreciation%20of%20the%20USD%2C%26quot%3B%20Laffer%20Jr.%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Stovall%2C%20about%2040%25%20of%20revenues%20from%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20companies%20come%20from%20overseas%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20higher%20dollar%20will%20likely%20result%20in%20lower%20profits%20from%20overseas%20operations%2C%20depressing%20the%20company's%20overall%20earnings%2C%26quot%3B%20Stovall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20profits%20could%20negatively%20impact%20the%20economy%20if%20the%20strong%20dollar%20move%20is%20sustained%20and%20economic%20growth%20doesn't%20make%20up%20for%20the%20shortfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20long%20run%2C%20this%20could%20result%20in%20an%20economic%20slowdown%2C%20which%20may%20jeopardize%20one's%20job%20at%20a%20company%20with%20many%20overseas%20clients.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20change%20in%20the%20value%20of%20the%20US%20dollar%20is%20typically%20a%20double-edged%20sword%2C%20helping%20your%20wallet%20in%20one%20way%20while%20adversely%20affecting%20your%20portfolio%20and%20livelihood%20in%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20Stovall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20dollar%20is%20higher%20since%20the%20election%2C%20it%20is%20still%20well%20below%20its%202022%20peak%20of%20nearly%20%24115%20and%202001%20peak%20of%20about%20%24120.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-dollar-strong-impact-consumer-prices-stock-market-investments-inflation-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732973402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d1ca78392a3bda9f237cb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fus-dollar-strong-impact-consumer-prices-stock-market-investments-inflation-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20US%20dollar%20surge%20%26quot%3Bis%20typically%20a%20double-edged%20sword%2C%20helping%20your%20wallet%20in%20one%20way%20while%20adversely%20affecting%20your%20portfolio%2C%26quot%3B%20Sam%20Stovall%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fus-dollar-strong-impact-consumer-prices-stock-market-investments-inflation-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222034%20World%20Cup%20can%20improve%20Saudi%20human%20rights%20-%20Fifa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732973334000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_sport%2Fe927%2Flive%2F2596b2c0-af12-11ef-bdf5-b7cb2fa86e10.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fc1545l4vnjgo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BBC%20sp