A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20reached%20over%2030%2C000%20children%20across%20175%20schools%20in%2016%20states.%20The%20group%E2%80%99s%20community%20libraries%20in%20cities%20like%20Kota%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20Delhi%2C%20housing%20more%20than%205%2C000%20books%2C%20recently%20welcomed%20232%20new%20members.%20SABIA%20also%20improved%20library%20spaces%20in%20schools%20across%20Delhi%20and%20Noida%2C%20and%20established%20its%20first%20model%20school%20library%20in%20Jaipur%20that%20houses%20books%20and%20serves%20as%20a%20space%20where%20children%20can%20learn%2C%20creatively%20engage%20themselves%20or%20study.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20organisation%20hosted%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311547%2Fdelhi-jasmine-anoop-start-storytelling-initiative-for-children-in-rural-himachal-pradesh-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estorytelling%20sessions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20public%20and%20low-budget%20private%20schools%20in%20and%20around%20Jaipur%2C%20conducted%20by%20a%20team%20of%2014%20storytellers.%20These%20sessions%20focused%20on%20perspective%2C%20empathy%2C%20and%20creative%20thinking%2C%20helping%20the%20children%20develop%20important%20life%20skills%20and%20a%20love%20for%20literature.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenges%2C%20and%20the%20road%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20challenges%20remain.%20The%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20highlighted%20the%20digital%20divide%20that%20exists%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20several%20children%20lacking%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20or%20technology%20for%20online%20learning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COut%20of%2025%2C000%20children%20we%20worked%20with%2C%20only%201%2C000%20could%20sign%20up%20for%20online%20sessions%2C%20and%20just%20300%20were%20regular%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srishti%20admits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20lockdown%20measures%20eased%2C%20SABIA%20managed%20to%20set%20up%20community%20spaces%20and%20adapt%20to%20the%20situation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20set%20up%20a%20library%20space%20in%20my%20own%20home%2C%20and%20later%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Jaipur%2C%20I%20opened%20a%20home%20library%20there%20too.%20This%20space%20was%20able%20to%20keep%20children%20engaged%20in%20learning%20even%20when%20their%20school%20had%20shut%20down%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srishti%2C%20recounting%20the%20story%20of%20Anita%20and%20Rani%20%E2%80%94%20two%20girls%20who%2C%20despite%20being%20out%20of%20school%20for%20years%20due%20to%20COVID%2C%20were%20able%20to%20catch%20up%20because%20they%20had%20a%20supportive%20learning%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202760px)%20100vw%2C%202760px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20girls%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20newly%20set%20up%20bookshelves%20in%20their%20school.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525.jpg%202760w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-768x577.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-1536x1153.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-2048x1537.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-1200x901.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-383826%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EModel%20Libraries%20serve%20as%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20students%20to%20learn%20and%20read%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20continue%20this%20work%2C%20SABIA%20relies%20on%20project-based%20funding%2C%20even%20during%20crowdfunding%20campaigns.%20They%20first%20identify%20schools%20that%20need%20help%20and%20then%20share%20their%20goals%20with%20the%20public%2C%20explaining%20how%20people%20can%20get%20involved.%20They%20also%20receive%20support%20through%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20(CSR)%20funding%2C%20where%20companies%20fund%20specific%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20Hindustan%20Petroleum%2C%20SABIA%20set%20up%20libraries%20in%2020%20schools%20in%20Kashmir.%20Government%20support%20has%20also%20been%20vital%2C%20granting%20permissions%20and%20providing%20access%20to%20schools%20in%20areas%20that%20need%20help%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20SABIA%20will%20be%20hosting%20a%20book%20fair%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20the%2013%20and%2014%20December%20at%20the%20YMCA%2C%20Andheri%2C%20to%20raise%20funds%20by%20selli