%80%99s%20struggles%2C%20only%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20problem%20had%20been%20the%20milk%20all%20along!%20%E2%80%9CPackaged%20and%20processed%20milk%20is%20a%20bad%20option%20for%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20local%20dairy%20farms%20fell%20short%20due%20to%20hygiene%20issues%20or%20subpar%20feed%20given%20to%20cows.%20Resolving%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20Jyoti%2C%20a%20textile%20engineering%20graduate%2C%20embarked%20on%20a%20self-learning%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20farming%20background.%20All%20that%20I%20have%20implemented%20is%20through%20trial-and-error%20and%20self-learning%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyoti%20set%20up%20her%20first%20farm%20in%20Lucknow%20with%2015%20mixed-breed%20cows%2C%20including%20Jerseys%20and%20Sahiwals.%20However%2C%20her%20limited%20knowledge%20of%20cow%20nutrition%20affected%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20milk.%20After%20relocating%20to%20Thane%2C%20Jyoti%20identified%20a%20pressing%20need%20for%20pure%20A2%20cow%20milk%20in%20urban%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20getting%20fresh%20milk%20was%20never%20a%20worry.%20When%20my%20daughter%20needed%20pure%20milk%20here%2C%20I%20realised%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20necessity%2C%20not%20a%20luxury%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20research%20study%20published%20in%20the%20National%20Library%20of%20Medicine%2C%20A2%20milk%20%E2%80%94%20milk%20that%20only%20contains%20a%20variant%20of%20beta-casein%20called%20A2%20%E2%80%94%20has%20on%20several%20occasions%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20lactose%20intolerant%20people.%20The%20difference%20in%20protein%20between%20the%20A2%20and%20A1%20varieties%20makes%20the%20former%20a%20more%20easily%20digestible%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20holistic%20approach%20to%20dairy%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Jyoti%20established%20Sree%20Balkrishna%20Dairy%20Farm%20(BKD%20Milk)%20on%20two%20acres%20of%20leased%20land%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Maharashtra.%20With%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20she%20envisioned%20a%20farm%20where%20cows%20would%20roam%20freely%2C%20nourished%20by%20organic%20feed%20like%205G%20Napier%20grass%2C%20wheatgrass%2C%20and%20millets.%20The%20focus%20was%20clear%3A%20to%20produce%20A2%20milk%2C%20free%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351820%2Ffive-composting-hacks-to-keep-your-plants-cool-in-the-summer-youtube-channel-heatwave%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadulteration%20and%20harmful%20chemicals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20strong%20advocate%20for%20ethical%20and%20humane%20farming%20practices%2C%20Jyoti%20insists%20on%20hand%20milking%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20milk%20reaches%20consumers%E2%80%99%20homes%20within%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CCertain%20farmers%20inject%20an%20injection%20worth%20Rs%2020%20to%20the%20cow%2C%20which%20affects%20the%20nervous%20system%2C%20causing%20the%20cow%20to%20produce%20milk%20for%2048%20hours%20straight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jyoti%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThis%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20causes%20harmful%20health%20issues%20for%20consumers%2C%20probing%20early%20changes%20like%20puberty%20way%20ahead%20of%20time.%20At%20BKD%20Milk%2C%20we%20prioritise%20the%20well-being%20of%20our%20cows%20and%20the%20purity%20of%20our%20milk.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg