ndia.com%2F299651%2Fconservationist-meera-chandran-quit-job-to-fight-invasive-plant-species-restore-forest-land%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremoval%20of%20invasive%20species.%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20grassroots%20efforts%2C%20Sharvan%20has%20made%20smart%20use%20of%20social%20media%20to%20amplify%20his%20cause%20and%20engage%20with%20a%20larger%20audience.%20His%20Instagram%20page%2C%20%E2%80%98Thar%20Desert%20Photography%E2%80%99%2C%20has%20become%20a%20platform%20for%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20issues%20facing%20wildlife%20in%20the%20region.%20Through%20this%2C%20he%20has%20successfully%20used%20hashtags%20like%20%23HiranBachao%2C%20%23SaveRiverJojri%2C%20and%20%23GodavarBachao%20to%20attract%20attention%20to%20his%20cause%2C%20even%20getting%20%23SaveRiverJojri%20to%20trend%20number%20one%20on%20Twitter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20more%20eyes%20we%20have%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20it%20is%20that%20someone%20will%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20recently%20passed%20Wildlife%20Week%2C%20they%20carried%20out%20a%20campaign%20where%20they%20made%20frames%20of%20various%20wild%20animals%20and%20plants%20and%20presented%20them%20to%20school%20classrooms%2C%20panchayat%20houses%2C%20and%20government%20offices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20go%20to%20schools%20and%20ask%20the%20children%20%E2%80%98what%20is%20wildlife%E2%80%99%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20zebras%2C%20tigers%2C%20or%20lions%2C%20even%20if%20the%20kids%20have%20never%20seen%20them.%20But%20if%20you%20ask%20someone%20to%20identify%20a%20bustard%2C%20not%20many%20will%20get%20it%20right.%20The%20local%20wildlife%2C%20because%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20eyes%20on%20it%2C%20is%20silently%20depleting.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20make%20the%20children%20a%20part%20of%20the%20conversation%20because%20they%20will%20have%20to%20take%20this%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jagdish%20Pooniya%2C%2032%2C%20an%20audit%20inspector%20from%20the%20Dhava%20Doli%20Wildlife%20area%2C%20and%20one%20of%20Sharvan%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20key%20collaborators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHands-on%20approach%20to%20wildlife%20conservation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20vital%20aspect%20of%20Sharvan%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20been%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20forest%20department%20and%20local%20government%20officials.%20As%20someone%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20the%20department%20for%20over%20five%20years%2C%20he%20has%20seen%20firsthand%20the%20challenges%20they%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20only%20one%20small%20room%20with%20one%20staff%20member%2C%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20means%20to%20help%20injured%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharvan%20explains.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20often%20step%20in%20to%20provide%20immediate%20assistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sharvan%20tending%20to%20an%20injured%20deer%2F%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette