es%20me%20that%20the%20direction%20I%20am%20taking%20%5Bcreatively%5D%20is%20good.%20Hopefully%2C%20this%20nomination%20fuels%20any%20independent%20artist%20out%20there%20to%20have%20a%20great%20and%20enriching%20creative%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMusic%20permeating%20through%20the%20walls%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarijashree%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%2C%20a%20master%20flautist%2C%20and%20my%20mother%2C%20T%20V%20Rama%2C%20an%20accomplished%20vocalist%2C%20were%20my%20first%20gurus.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20everything%20started%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20memories%20as%20a%20toddler%20are%20few%2C%20but%20they%20come%20back%20to%20her%20in%20flashes.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20vividly%20remember%20sitting%20through%20%3Cem%3EAppa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20(father)%20flute%20lessons%20that%20he%20would%20give%20to%20students%20at%20home%20(he%20still%20avidly%20teaches%20to%20this%20day).%20Just%20being%20inside%20the%20house%2C%20I%20remember%20how%20the%20sound%20of%20my%20father%20playing%20the%20flute%20used%20to%20permeate%20the%20walls%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varijashree%20is%20a%20grammy-nominated%20artist%20%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669