ndia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382707%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20Jazz%20al%20Parque%20Festival%20in%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%20Colombia.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20have%20discovered%20during%20my%20journey%20as%20a%20seeker%20of%20new%20sounds%20is%20the%20art%20of%20writing%20my%20own%20music.%20I%20have%20created%20it%20in%20small%20bits%20and%20pieces%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20a%20single%20here%20or%20there%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20have%20always%20dreamed%20of%20composing%20a%20longer%20piece%2C%20like%20a%20full-length%20album.%20Despite%20my%20aspirations%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20like%20something%20that%20would%20happen%20anytime%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20one%20of%20my%20travels%2C%20I%20met%20Michael%20League%2C%20the%20Grammy-winning%20founder%20of%20Snarky%20Puppy.%20This%20was%20about%20eight%20or%20nine%20years%20ago%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289488%2Fnew-york-best-chef-chintan-pandya-indian-food-begun-bhaja-champaran-meat-in-america%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20we%20attended%20a%20Roy%20Haynes%20concert%20at%20the%20Blue%20Note.%20Afterwards%2C%20we%20kept%20in%20touch.%20I%20showed%20him%20a%20couple%20of%20songs%20I%20had%20begun%20writing%2C%20and%20he%20was%20very%20encouraging%2C%20suggesting%